long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Don’t stream alone! StarSearch™ by Real® is a powerful must-have YouTube and Netflix companion to instantly identify celebs with one click. It answers the question, “Hey, who is that?” and opens up a world of fun.

Click on a video with visible faces, StarSearch immediately goes into action. It even uncovers fun celebrity facts and related videos to deepen your experience!

Browse the most popular videos, and StarSearch instantly shows which celebs are in a video and where they appear. StarSearch automatically generates a visual table of contents by faces. You can immediately jump through the timeline to spot people.

StarSearch is fast, fun, friendly, and free!

Install StarSearch today and expect more from your videos!
